    'introduce_len' => '0',
    'content' => '<p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2017年8月7日，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">位于阳泉盂县水神山的报国寺阳光明媚，明亮清净。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在佛菩萨的加持下，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">报国寺首届佛教文化体验夏令营活动顺利开营。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022910367791.jpg" title="15022910367791.jpg" alt="14.jpg" width="589" height="324" style="width: 589px; height: 324px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">出席本次夏令营开营仪式的有：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国佛教协会理事，山西省佛教协会副会长，山西省政协委员，阳泉市佛教协会常务副会长，阳泉市人大代表，盂县永清寺，报国寺方丈一度大和尚；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">天津市津南区政协委员，天津市华盛寺住持，五台山碧山寺西堂（管理相关寺务）达云法师；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">盂县佛教协会会长<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;">一军法师；</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，寂光法师、义圆法师、义泰法师、汇成法师、正亮法师、汇宣法师、邹成海先生等也参加了开营仪式。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022910843242.jpg" title="15022910843242.jpg" alt="16.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">早上八点，开营仪式正式开始，由达云法师主持。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022911474044.jpg" title="15022911474044.jpg" alt="17.jpg" width="602" height="453" style="width: 602px; height: 453px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一度大和尚开示</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">大和尚说道：“大家都是从五湖四海过来的，报国寺举办“不忘初心”佛教体验夏令营活动，是希望大家记住自己的那颗初心，即改变自己不好的生活习惯。通过师父们的教导，让大家可以领悟到佛法的奥妙和乐趣。因此希望大家都能用心去感受。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">报国寺四面环山，当时起这个名字的缘起也是为了教导众生能够真正做到报国。报国寺占地170多亩，从僧众们买地到发心建成花了四年的时间，这种建立的方式在山西省是第一个。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">由于报国寺的地理位置，南方的营员应该能感受到这里的清凉。所以希望大家能在这里好好发心，不忘初心，营员的初心就是报名时的初心，希望大家都能够坚持下来。</span><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">”</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022912198720.jpg" title="15022912198720.jpg" alt="18.jpg"/></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">盂县佛教协会会长一军法师为大家开示：“欢迎的到来，佛教有句话叫做“人身难得，佛法难闻。”我们有很多营员都是刚领悟到佛法，所以希望大家能珍惜这次机会，有信仰的人是幸福的，预祝报国寺首届夏令营成功举办。”</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022912565356.jpg" title="15022912565356.jpg" alt="19.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">义圆法师开示：“很高兴大家能够来参加报国寺第一届夏令营活动，“万事开头难”，希望各位营员们能给大家带个好头，可能今后报国寺会因为你们而面向全国招营员，度化更多人。”</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022912851079.jpg" title="15022912851079.jpg" alt="20.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">义泰法师为大家开示：“7天时间不长，但是会在我们心中播撒出一个种子，感受佛法带来的智慧。这样的机会看似很容易，实则很难得。希望大家能利用时间用心去体会，7天后有所收获。”</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022913806001.jpg" title="15022913806001.jpg" alt="21.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">寂礼居士作为本次夏令营活动的男众营员代表做了发言。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“今天有缘聚在一起，感恩佛菩萨，感恩一度大和尚，感恩法师，感恩义工，感恩……因为我之前有了失眠症，所以在听了很多歌曲都没有效果的情况下，是佛歌《药师咒》帮我缓解了失眠的痛苦。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">自此我开始对佛教产生兴趣，去年6月份在报国寺皈依。后来在汇宣法师的鼓励下报名参加，非常感恩，所以一切化成一句阿弥陀佛。”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022914383150.png" title="15022914383150.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">高序芬作为女众代表进行了发言。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px;">“感谢大和尚让人们有机会来这里亲近佛法，这是我第一次来山西，皈依有两年了，一直没有机会去体验佛教真实的生活，后来在老家朋友的推荐下才机会来到这里，所以十分感恩。在与义工接触的这几天，最深的感悟就是，人一定要学会利他，这样才不负此生。”</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022914754414.png" title="15022914754414.png" alt="blob.png"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">义工代表的发言朴实真切。她说道：“感恩一度大和尚，感恩师父能为众生“表法”，希望在这里每个人都能得到改变，感受到无量光明，清净清法。”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022915552905.jpg" title="15022915552905.jpg" alt="22.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">随后，一度大和尚宣布“报国寺首届佛教文化体验夏令营活动”正式开营，并授营旗，营员代表接过营旗挥舞，报国寺首届佛教文化体验夏令营正式开营！</span><span style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.75em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">至此，在庄严的《三宝歌》中，</span><span style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.75em;">阳泉盂县报国寺首届佛教文化体验夏令营活动开营仪式圆满！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p>',
