    'image' => '/',
    'thumb' => '/upload/images/201708/15022885851864.jpg',
    'state' => '1',
    'checked' => '1',
    'introduce' => '按照国家宗教事务局和中国佛教协会“关于积极开展汉传佛教讲经交流活动”的有关精神，结合中国佛教协会关于2017中国佛教讲经交流会安排，由山西省佛教协会主办，阳泉市佛教协会、盂县佛教协会、盂县报国寺承办，以“慈悲·圆融·宏博”为主题的山西省第四届佛教讲经交流活动于2017年8月3日在阳泉盂县报国寺拉开帷幕。',
    'introduce_len' => '0',
    'content' => '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">按照国家宗教事务局和中国佛教协会“关于积极开展汉传佛教讲经交流活动”的有关精神，结合中国佛教协会关于2017中国佛教讲经交流会安排，由山西省佛教协会主办，阳泉市佛教协会、盂县佛教协会、盂县报国寺承办，以“慈悲·圆融·宏博”为主题的山西省第四届佛教讲经交流活动于2017年8月3日在阳泉盂县报国寺拉开帷幕。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022892403751.jpg" title="15022892403751.jpg" alt="201701.jpg"/></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8月3日</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">上午，开幕仪式前，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">隆重</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">举行了诵经祈福法会，中国佛教协会副会长、山西省佛教协会会长妙江法师，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国佛教协会藏传南传佛教办公室主任清远法师，山西省佛教协会副会长、</span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">五台山佛教协会会长昌善法师三位法师共同拈香主法。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022892929605.jpg" title="15022892929605.jpg" alt="01.jpg"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国佛教协会副会长、山西省佛教协会会长妙江法师拈香主法</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022893353255.jpg" title="15022893353255.jpg" alt="02.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国佛教协会藏传南传佛教办公室主任清远法师，山西省佛教协会副会长、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">五台山佛教协会会长昌善法师拈香主法</span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 上午9时，2017山西省第四届佛教讲经交流大会开幕式在庄严的国歌声中拉开帷幕，出席此次讲经交流会开幕式的有：山西省人大常委会民族宗教侨务外事工作委员会副主任王尚义，山西省政协民族宗教委员会巡视员王建国，山西省宗教事务局副局长侯文禄，阳泉市委常委、市委统战部部长王铁梅，阳泉市委常委、盂县县委书记李云峰，阳泉市人大副主任张宝明先生，阳泉市政协副主席王良义，中国佛教协会副会长、山西省佛教协会会长妙江法师，中国佛教协会副会长、山西省佛教协会副会长如瑞法师，中国佛教协会藏传南传佛教办公室主任清远法师，山西省佛教协会副会长兼秘书长法海法师，山西省佛教协会副会长、五台山佛教协会会长昌善法师，山西省佛教协会副会长国亮法师，山西省佛教协会副会长、五台山佛教协会副会长如空法师，中国佛协理事、山西省佛教协会副会长、阳泉市佛教协会常务副会长、永清寺方丈一度大和尚，山西省佛教协会副会长、五台山佛教协会副会长海信法师，五台山佛教协会副会长兼秘书长悲月法师，五台山佛教协会副会长能戒法师以及省宗教局、省佛教协会、各市县佛协有关领导，居士等。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896415489.jpg" title="15022896415489.jpg" alt="03.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896518578.jpg" title="15022896518578.jpg" alt="04.jpg" width="581" height="363" style="width: 581px; height: 363px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">开幕式由中国佛教协会副会长、山西省佛教协会会长妙江法师主持</span></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896693298.jpg" title="15022896693298.jpg" alt="05.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阳泉市委常委、市委统战部部长王铁梅致辞</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896809025.jpg" title="15022896809025.jpg" alt="06.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">山西省宗教事务局副局长侯文禄讲话</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896909952.jpg" title="15022896909952.jpg" alt="08.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国佛协理事、山西省佛教协会副会长、阳泉市佛教协会常务副会长、永清寺方丈一度大和尚在主席台就座</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022896987189.jpg" title="15022896987189.jpg" alt="09.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">山西省佛协副会长国亮法师介绍活动安排、评比标准、评委情况</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022897066699.jpg" title="15022897066699.jpg" alt="10.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国佛教协会副会长，山西省佛教协会副会长，五台山尼众佛学院院长如瑞法师做示范讲经</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">汇性法师和汇清法师代表报国寺参加本次讲经交流会，汇山法师代表玉佛寺参加本次讲经交流会。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022897973064.jpg" title="15022897973064.jpg" alt="13.jpg"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阳泉报国寺汇清法师围绕如何利益众生之《大方广佛华严经普贤行愿品》进行主题宣讲</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022897367750.jpg" title="15022897367750.jpg" alt="11.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阳泉玉佛寺汇山法师围绕如何利益众生进行主题宣讲</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201708/15022897522330.jpg" title="15022897522330.jpg" alt="12.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">阳泉报国寺汇性法师围绕如何认识因果进行主题宣讲</span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> &nbsp; &nbsp;从2013年以来，山西省佛教协会已经连续举办三次讲经交流会，通过举办讲经交流，带动和形成我省佛教四众弟子读诵经典、研习经典、讲解经典的良好风气，更好的发挥我们佛教这一中华优秀传统文化的特殊作用，紧跟“一带一路”文化发展思路。</span></strong></span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 24.5px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p>',
