    'introduce' => '2017年8月2日至4日，山西省第四届佛教讲经交流会将在阳泉市盂县报国寺举办。本次活动主题为：“慈悲·圆融·宏博”。',
    'introduce_len' => '0',
    'content' => '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2017年8月2日至4日，山西省第四届佛教讲经交流会将在阳泉市盂县报国寺举办。</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">本次活动主题为：“慈悲·圆融·宏博”。</span></strong></span><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);">&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px;"><span style="line-height: 25.6px;">宣讲内容分为：如何安顿身心？如何建立信仰？如何认识因果？如何利益众生？如何依教修学？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">讲经所依大乘经典包括《金刚般若波罗蜜经》、《般若波罗蜜多心经》、《佛说阿弥陀经》等十六部。</span></span></span><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">宣讲法师依止经典，从生活中出发，结合实修，对生命形态发起种种思考，深入浅出引领我们走向解脱不可思议境界、其语言丰富，自然，通俗，易懂。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6;">随着我们山西省佛教讲经交流会的成功举办，不仅能树立佛教界勤学修行、服务社会的良好形象，也能从中发现了一大批优秀的佛教后继僧才，进一步推动全省佛教的有序发展。</span></span></span></strong></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> 讲经交流会期间，山西报国寺欢迎众居士信众随缘参加，一睹演讲法师风采，参悟生命真谛。</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></strong></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">主办：山西省佛教协会</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">承办：阳泉市佛教协会、盂县佛教协会</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15014236224610.jpg" title="15014236224610.jpg" alt="211.jpg" width="606" height="402" style="width: 606px; height: 402px;"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong style="font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">期间，报国</strong><strong style="font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">寺将隆重举办大型音乐文艺晚会</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">山西省佛教协会主办的第四届山西省汉传佛教讲经交流大会，将于2017年8月2起至4日在阳泉盂县报国寺举办，届时，全省各地300余位高僧大德前来参会，开展讲经交流比赛，在此期间“报国寺佛音四海合唱团”将与“阳泉市文化艺术学校”联合献上高雅的文艺晚会。“报国寺佛音四海合唱团”将首次献上由我国著名作曲家甘霖老师创作的五首佛教励志歌曲！欢迎广大信众前来观看！愿我们的演出能与您结缘，愿慧灯朗朗永远普照众生！</span></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;演 出 时 间：8月3日晚8时&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 演 出 地 点：报国寺广场</strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15014243836680.jpg" title="15014243836680.jpg" alt="023.jpg" width="686" height="499" style="width: 686px; height: 499px;"/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15014246725007.jpg" title="15014246725007.jpg" alt="240.jpg"/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15014247703772.jpg" title="15014247703772.jpg" alt="250.jpg"/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 20px; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为更好承事三宝事业，使得这次讲经和晚会取得圆满成功，报国寺义工团现向社会有志人士发出邀请，招募此次活动义工。</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">做义工对我们修学的帮助：</strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1、<span style="color: rgb(37, 37, 37); line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;">量大福大，心心念的是团体的需要，为寺院而做义工，为护持佛教，弘扬佛法而做义工，为世界和平，众生安乐而做义工，这就是以我们的“身、口、意”大做供养、大行布施，不求回报也自然增长无量无边的福报和功德。</span></strong></span></strong><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2、开智慧，通过在寺院学习做义工，既增长自己的见识和各种工作能力，又使自己体会义工团体与社会上的其他团体所经历的工作过程的不同，义工们和合增上、快乐的工作心态与世俗工作中各种勾心斗角、争权夺利的心态的不同，使自己懂得如何选择人生道路、照顾心态，健康快乐地生活。</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHe