    'content' => '<p><span style="font-size: 20px;">为全面落实全民健身国家战略，推动体育与旅游的融合发展，7月7日-9日，由盂县县委、县政府、阳泉市体育局主办，盂县文化局、盂县文物旅游局、阳泉市摩托车运动协会承办的“星耀摩旅 清凉盂县”——2017第五届摩托人阳泉盛典暨盂县摩旅文化节系列活动在盂县举办。为参与此次活动，报国寺在汇成法师带领下，组织了以“心净则国土净”接待活动，活动分为前行、正行和结行，大众踊跃参与，践行了报国寺“依教行，不观过，共修学”的弘法精神，让摩旅参与者沐浴佛恩，让护法义工学习了皈依三宝，广结善缘佛法知识，大众无不欢喜，修行也多了更多实操，3天接待工作，报国寺共接待了316名骑手。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 24px;">前行</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001884645369.jpg" title="15001884645369.jpg" alt="006.jpg" width="579" height="404" style="width: 579px; height: 404px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">教化部同行善友与师谐行</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001884404541.jpg" title="15001884404541.jpg" alt="020.jpg" width="580" height="383" style="width: 580px; height: 383px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">师者，率先垂范。身教胜于言教。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">正行</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001885855904.jpg" title="15001885855904.jpg" alt="008.jpg" width="585" height="404" style="width: 585px; height: 404px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">你要知道广结善缘的重要，2017，我们报国寺义工全体践行“广结善缘”行动！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001886381641.jpg" title="15001886381641.jpg" alt="009.jpg" width="582" height="388" style="width: 582px; height: 388px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">留念，我们同圆种智，南无阿弥陀佛</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001887247994.jpg" title="15001887247994.jpg" alt="00212.jpg" width="584" height="386" style="width: 584px; height: 386px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">践行菩萨道，因上努力，果上随缘。二组组长说，我们很普通，因为我们很实在，没有虚伪，清凉自在。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><span style="font-size: 24px;">结行</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001887799121.jpg" title="15001887799121.jpg" alt="011.jpg" width="585" height="412" style="width: 585px; height: 412px;"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三天的接待工作，学习皈依三宝的功德利益等诸多佛学知识！</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><img src="/upload/images/201707/15001888583753.jpg" title="15001888583753.jpg" alt="012.jpg" width="590" height="367" style="width: 590px; height: 367px;"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为了大家，也为了自己，为了三宝住世，都是快乐善行！</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">三天的接待工作完毕后，报国寺住持汇成法师慈悲感恩,在本寺斋堂举行了答谢会！</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">住持开示说：感恩诸位信徒,义工的辛苦护法，义工们都在任劳任怨的时候，身教胜于言教。义工、居士都是寺院的形象，感恩，我们义工所做的每一件事情！</span></strong></span></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 住持开示说：感恩诸位信徒,义工的辛苦护法，义工们都在任劳任怨的时候！</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp; &nbsp; 住持开示说：感恩诸位信徒,义工的辛苦护法，义工们都在任劳任怨的时候，身教胜于言教。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">感恩的盛宴！再次感恩我们的师父，感恩三宝，感恩佛菩萨，感恩僧团，感恩汇成法师拉拔我们一路前行，感恩同行善友，感恩父母有情，是你们让我明白存在的价值，南无阿弥佗佛。</span></strong></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>',
